{
  "video_id": "N3SQlrmV1cE",
  "title": "The global goals we've made progress on -- and the ones we haven't | Michael Green",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12480.0,
      "end_time": 17976.0,
      "text": "In 2015, the leaders of the world made a big promise."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18000.0,
      "end_time": 20736.0,
      "text": "A promise that over the next 15 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20760.0,
      "end_time": 24336.0,
      "text": "the lives of billions of people are going to get better"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24360.0,
      "end_time": 26439.0,
      "text": "with no one left behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27200.0,
      "end_time": 30416.0,
      "text": "That promise is the Sustainable Development Goals --"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30440.0,
      "end_time": 31640.0,
      "text": "the SDGs."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32479.0,
      "end_time": 34296.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re now three years in;"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34320.0,
      "end_time": 36656.0,
      "text": "a fifth of the way into the journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36680.0,
      "end_time": 38376.0,
      "text": "The clock is ticking."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38400.0,
      "end_time": 39936.0,
      "text": "If we offtrack now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39960.0,
      "end_time": 43200.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s going to get harder and harder to hit those goals."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44320.0,
      "end_time": 47960.0,
      "text": "So what I want to do for you today is give you a snapshot"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47120.0,
      "end_time": 48855.0,
      "text": "on where we are today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48880.0,
      "end_time": 52160.0,
      "text": "some projections on where we&#39;re heading"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 52400.0,
      "end_time": 55600.0,
      "text": "and some ideas on things we might need to do differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 57440.0,
      "end_time": 61256.0,
      "text": "Now, the SDGs are of course spectacularly complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 61280.0,
      "end_time": 63736.0,
      "text": "I would expect nothing less from the United Nations."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63760.0,
      "end_time": 64775.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64800.0,
      "end_time": 66150.0,
      "text": "How many goals?"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 66400.0,
      "end_time": 69856.0,
      "text": "Maybe something tried and tested, like three, seven or 10."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69880.0,
      "end_time": 73295.0,
      "text": "No, let&#39;s pick a prime number higher than 10."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73320.0,
      "end_time": 75390.0,
      "text": "Seventeen goals."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 75960.0,
      "end_time": 78895.0,
      "text": "I congratulate those of you who&#39;ve memorized them already."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 78920.0,
      "end_time": 81560.0,
      "text": "For the rest of us, here they are."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 81800.0,
      "end_time": 84960.0,
      "text": "Seventeen goals ranging from ending poverty"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 84120.0,
      "end_time": 85496.0,
      "text": "to inclusive cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 85520.0,
      "end_time": 87336.0,
      "text": "to sustainable fisheries;"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 87360.0,
      "end_time": 90800.0,
      "text": "all a comprehensive plan for the future of our world."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 91720.0,
      "end_time": 95440.0,
      "text": "But sadly, a plan without the data to measure it."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 96280.0,
      "end_time": 98900.0,
      "text": "So how are we going to track progress?"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 98880.0,
      "end_time": 102776.0,
      "text": "Well, I&#39;m going to use today the Social Progress Index."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 102800.0,
      "end_time": 105896.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a measure of the quality of life of countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 105920.0,
      "end_time": 108936.0,
      "text": "ranging from the basic needs of survival --"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 108960.0,
      "end_time": 111735.0,
      "text": "food, water, shelter, safety --"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 111760.0,
      "end_time": 114160.0,
      "text": "through to the foundations of well-being --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 114400.0,
      "end_time": 117376.0,
      "text": "education, information, health and the environment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 117400.0,
      "end_time": 118976.0,
      "text": "and opportunity --"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 119000.0,
      "end_time": 124000.0,
      "text": "rights, freedom of choice, inclusiveness and access to higher education."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 125240.0,
      "end_time": 128735.0,
      "text": "Now, the Social Progress Index doesn&#39;t look like the SDGs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128758.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132960.0,
      "text": "but fundamentally, it&#39;s measuring the same concepts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 132120.0,
      "end_time": 135696.0,
      "text": "and the Social Progress Index has the advantage that we have the data."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 135720.0,
      "end_time": 138976.0,
      "text": "We have 51 indicators drawn from trusted sources"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 139000.0,
      "end_time": 140440.0,
      "text": "to measure these concepts."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 141479.0,
      "end_time": 144560.0,
      "text": "And also, what we can do because it&#39;s an index,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 144800.0,
      "end_time": 147976.0,
      "text": "is add together all those indicators to give us an aggregate score"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 148000.0,
      "end_time": 152800.0,
      "text": "about how we&#39;re performing against the total package of the SDGs."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 153120.0,
      "end_time": 154576.0,
      "text": "Now, one caveat."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 154600.0,
      "end_time": 157456.0,
      "text": "The Social Progress Index is a measure of quality of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 157480.0,
      "end_time": 159816.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re not looking at whether this can be achieved"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 159840.0,
      "end_time": 161816.0,
      "text": "within the planet&#39;s environmental limits."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 161840.0,
      "end_time": 163640.0,
      "text": "You will need other tools to do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 165200.0,
      "end_time": 167679.0,
      "text": "So how are we doing on the SDGs?"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 168320.0,
      "end_time": 172616.0,
      "text": "Well, I&#39;m going to put the SDGs on a scale of zero to 100."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 172640.0,
      "end_time": 177550.0,
      "text": "And zero is the absolute worst score on each of those 51 indicators:"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 177800.0,
      "end_time": 179576.0,
      "text": "absolute social progress, zero."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 179600.0,
      "end_time": 184696.0,
      "text": "And then 100 is the minimum standard required to achieve those SDGs."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 184720.0,
      "end_time": 187600.0,
      "text": "A hundred is where we want to get to by 2030."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 188600.0,
      "end_time": 190816.0,
      "text": "So, where did we start on this journey?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 190840.0,
      "end_time": 192736.0,
      "text": "Fortunately, not at zero."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 192760.0,
      "end_time": 198856.0,
      "text": "In 2015, the world score against the SDGs was 69.1."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 198880.0,
      "end_time": 201640.0,
      "text": "Some way on the way there but quite a long way to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 202320.0,
      "end_time": 204936.0,
      "text": "Now let me also emphasize that this world forecast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 204960.0,
      "end_time": 207336.0,
      "text": "which is based on data from 180 countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 207360.0,
      "end_time": 209560.0,
      "text": "is population weighted."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 209800.0,
      "end_time": 211536.0,
      "text": "So China has more weight in than Comoros;"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 211560.0,
      "end_time": 213440.0,
      "text": "India has more weight in than Iceland."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 214800.0,
      "end_time": 217936.0,
      "text": "But we could unpack this and see how the countries are doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 217960.0,
      "end_time": 223576.0,
      "text": "And the country today that is closest to achieving the SDGs is Denmark."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 223600.0,
      "end_time": 227200.0,
      "text": "And the country with the furthest to go is Central African Republic."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 227920.0,
      "end_time": 230519.0,
      "text": "And everyone else is somewhere in between."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 231595.0,
      "end_time": 232976.0,
      "text": "So the challenge for the SDGs"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 233000.0,
      "end_time": 238280.0,
      "text": "is to try and sweep all these dots across to the right, to 100 by 2030."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 239120.0,
      "end_time": 240320.0,
      "text": "Can we get there?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 241400.0,
      "end_time": 244376.0,
      "text": "Well, with the Social Progress Index, we&#39;ve got some time series data."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 244400.0,
      "end_time": 247696.0,
      "text": "So we have some idea of the trend that the countries are on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 247720.0,
      "end_time": 250200.0,
      "text": "on which we can build some projections."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 250880.0,
      "end_time": 252960.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s have a look."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252120.0,
      "end_time": 255136.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start with our top-performing country, Denmark."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 255160.0,
      "end_time": 260120.0,
      "text": "And yes, I&#39;m pleased to say that Denmark is forecast to achieve the SDGs by 2030."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 260800.0,
      "end_time": 263936.0,
      "text": "Maybe not surprising, but I&#39;ll take a win."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 263960.0,
      "end_time": 267150.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look at some of the other richer countries of the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 267400.0,
      "end_time": 268255.0,
      "text": "the G7."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 268279.0,
      "end_time": 272360.0,
      "text": "And we find that Germany and Japan will get there or thereabouts."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 273790.0,
      "end_time": 279496.0,
      "text": "But Canada, France, the UK and Italy are all going to fall short."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 279520.0,
      "end_time": 281256.0,
      "text": "And the United States?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 281280.0,
      "end_time": 282520.0,
      "text": "Quite some way back."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 283880.0,
      "end_time": 286616.0,
      "text": "Now, this is sort of worrying news."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 286640.0,
      "end_time": 289150.0,
      "text": "But these are the richest countries in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 289400.0,
      "end_time": 290856.0,
      "text": "not the most populous."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 290880.0,
      "end_time": 293856.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s take a look now at the biggest countries in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 293880.0,
      "end_time": 297216.0,
      "text": "the ones that will most affect whether or not we achieve the SDGs."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 297240.0,
      "end_time": 298656.0,
      "text": "And here they are --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 298680.0,
      "end_time": 301896.0,
      "text": "countries in the world with a population of higher than 100 million,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 301920.0,
      "end_time": 303976.0,
      "text": "ranging from China to Ethiopia."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 304000.0,
      "end_time": 306496.0,
      "text": "Obviously, the US and Japan would be in that list,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 306520.0,
      "end_time": 308135.0,
      "text": "but we&#39;ve looked at them already."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 308160.0,
      "end_time": 309376.0,
      "text": "So here we are."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 309400.0,
      "end_time": 312936.0,
      "text": "The biggest countries in the world; the dealbreakers for the SDGs."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 312960.0,
      "end_time": 316656.0,
      "text": "And the country that&#39;s going to make most progress towards the SDGs"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 316680.0,
      "end_time": 318816.0,
      "text": "is Mexico."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 318840.0,
      "end_time": 320856.0,
      "text": "Mexico is going to get to about 87,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 320880.0,
      "end_time": 323256.0,
      "text": "so just shy of where the US is going to get"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 323280.0,
      "end_time": 325479.0,
      "text": "but quite some way off our SDG target."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 326160.0,
      "end_time": 327936.0,
      "text": "Russia comes next."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 327960.0,
      "end_time": 330575.0,
      "text": "Then China and Indonesia."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 330600.0,
      "end_time": 333656.0,
      "text": "Then Brazil -- might&#39;ve expected Brazil to do a bit better."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 333680.0,
      "end_time": 334976.0,
      "text": "Philippines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 335000.0,
      "end_time": 340416.0,
      "text": "and then a step down to India, Bangladesh, Pakistan, Nigeria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 340440.0,
      "end_time": 341719.0,
      "text": "and then Ethiopia."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 342960.0,
      "end_time": 346296.0,
      "text": "So none of these countries are going to hit the SDGs."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 346320.0,
      "end_time": 349536.0,
      "text": "And we can then take these numbers in all the countries of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 349560.0,
      "end_time": 351376.0,
      "text": "to give ourselves a world forecast"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 351400.0,
      "end_time": 354296.0,
      "text": "on achieving that total package of the SDGs."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 354320.0,
      "end_time": 358976.0,
      "text": "So remember, in 2015 we started at 69.1."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 359000.0,
      "end_time": 361376.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m pleased to say that over the last three years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 361400.0,
      "end_time": 362895.0,
      "text": "we have made some progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 362920.0,
      "end_time": 366320.0,
      "text": "In 2018, we&#39;ve hit 70.5,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 367160.0,
      "end_time": 370416.0,
      "text": "and if we project that rate of progress forward to 2030,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 370440.0,
      "end_time": 373240.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s going to get us to 75.2,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 373960.0,
      "end_time": 377120.0,
      "text": "which is obviously a long way short of our target."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 377880.0,
      "end_time": 384280.0,
      "text": "Indeed, on current trends, we won&#39;t hit the 2030 targets until 2094."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 386360.0,
      "end_time": 387736.0,
      "text": "Now, I don&#39;t know about you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 387760.0,
      "end_time": 390135.0,
      "text": "but I certainly don&#39;t want to wait that long."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 390160.0,
      "end_time": 391560.0,
      "text": "So what can we do about this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 392480.0,
      "end_time": 395896.0,
      "text": "Well, the first thing to do is we&#39;ve got to call out the rich countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 395920.0,
      "end_time": 398736.0,
      "text": "Here are the countries closest to the SDGs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 398760.0,
      "end_time": 400456.0,
      "text": "with the greatest resources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 400480.0,
      "end_time": 401760.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re falling short."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 402440.0,
      "end_time": 405336.0,
      "text": "Maybe they think that this is like the Old World"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 405360.0,
      "end_time": 409136.0,
      "text": "where goals for the UN are just for poor countries and not for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 409160.0,
      "end_time": 410376.0,
      "text": "Well, you&#39;re wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 410400.0,
      "end_time": 412496.0,
      "text": "The SDGs are for every country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 412520.0,
      "end_time": 415616.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s shameful that these wealthy countries are falling short."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 415640.0,
      "end_time": 418536.0,
      "text": "Every country needs a plan to implement the SDGs"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 418560.0,
      "end_time": 420456.0,
      "text": "and deliver them for their citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 420480.0,
      "end_time": 422536.0,
      "text": "G7, other rich countries --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 422560.0,
      "end_time": 423760.0,
      "text": "get your act together."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 425160.0,
      "end_time": 428576.0,
      "text": "The second thing we can do is look a bit further into the data"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 428600.0,
      "end_time": 431696.0,
      "text": "and see where there are opportunities to accelerate progress"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 431720.0,
      "end_time": 434240.0,
      "text": "or there are negative trends that we can reverse."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 435000.0,
      "end_time": 437560.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to take you into three areas."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 437800.0,
      "end_time": 439176.0,
      "text": "One where we&#39;re doing quite well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 439200.0,
      "end_time": 441455.0,
      "text": "one where we really should be doing better"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 441480.0,
      "end_time": 443880.0,
      "text": "and another where we&#39;ve got some real problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 445400.0,
      "end_time": 447150.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start with the good news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 447400.0,
      "end_time": 451336.0,
      "text": "and I want to talk about what we call nutrition and basic medical care."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 451360.0,
      "end_time": 453816.0,
      "text": "This covers SDG 2 on no hunger"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 453840.0,
      "end_time": 456176.0,
      "text": "and the basic elements of SDG 3 on health,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 456200.0,
      "end_time": 460616.0,
      "text": "so maternal and child mortality, infectious diseases, etc ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 460640.0,
      "end_time": 464816.0,
      "text": "This is an area where most of the rich world has hit the SDGs."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 464840.0,
      "end_time": 467376.0,
      "text": "And we also find, looking at our big countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 467400.0,
      "end_time": 470536.0,
      "text": "that the most advanced have got pretty close."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 470560.0,
      "end_time": 472536.0,
      "text": "Here are our 11 big countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 472560.0,
      "end_time": 473896.0,
      "text": "and if you look at the top,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 473920.0,
      "end_time": 476976.0,
      "text": "Brazil and Russia are pretty close to the SDG target."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 477000.0,
      "end_time": 478256.0,
      "text": "But at the bottom --"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 478280.0,
      "end_time": 480575.0,
      "text": "Ethiopia, Pakistan -- a long way to go."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 480600.0,
      "end_time": 482376.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s where we are in 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 482400.0,
      "end_time": 483655.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s our trajectory?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 483680.0,
      "end_time": 485336.0,
      "text": "On the current trajectory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 485360.0,
      "end_time": 487776.0,
      "text": "how far are we going to get by 2030?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 487800.0,
      "end_time": 489136.0,
      "text": "Well, let&#39;s have a look."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 489160.0,
      "end_time": 491896.0,
      "text": "Well, what we see is a lot of progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 491920.0,
      "end_time": 493616.0,
      "text": "See Bangladesh in the middle."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 493640.0,
      "end_time": 496695.0,
      "text": "If Bangladesh maintains its current rate of progress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 496720.0,
      "end_time": 499816.0,
      "text": "it could get very close to that SDG target."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 499840.0,
      "end_time": 503296.0,
      "text": "And Ethiopia at the bottom is making a huge amount of progress"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 503320.0,
      "end_time": 504536.0,
      "text": "at the moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 504560.0,
      "end_time": 507720.0,
      "text": "If that can be maintained, Ethiopia could get a long way."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 508640.0,
      "end_time": 511135.0,
      "text": "We add this all up for all the countries of the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 511160.0,
      "end_time": 516856.0,
      "text": "and our projection is a score of 94.5 by 2030."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 516880.0,
      "end_time": 520960.0,
      "text": "And if countries like the Philippines, which have grown more slowly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 520120.0,
      "end_time": 521416.0,
      "text": "could accelerate progress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 521440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523776.00000000006,
      "text": "then we could get a lot closer."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 523799.0,
      "end_time": 527760.0,
      "text": "So there are reasons to be optimistic about SDGs 2 and 3."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 528480.0,
      "end_time": 532856.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s another very basic area of the SDGs where we&#39;re doing less well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 532880.0,
      "end_time": 535880.0,
      "text": "which is SDG 6, on water and sanitation."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 536560.0,
      "end_time": 539295.0,
      "text": "Again, it&#39;s an SDG where most of the rich countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 539320.0,
      "end_time": 541256.0,
      "text": "have already achieved the targets."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 541280.0,
      "end_time": 542976.0,
      "text": "And again, for our big countries --"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 543000.0,
      "end_time": 545136.0,
      "text": "our big 11 emerging countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 545160.0,
      "end_time": 547896.0,
      "text": "we see that some of the countries, like Russia and Mexico,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 547920.0,
      "end_time": 550160.0,
      "text": "are very close to the target,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 550400.0,
      "end_time": 553719.0,
      "text": "but Nigeria and other countries are a very long way back."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 554440.0,
      "end_time": 556336.0,
      "text": "So how are we doing on this target?"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 556360.0,
      "end_time": 559536.0,
      "text": "What progress are we going to make over the next 12 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 559560.0,
      "end_time": 561520.0,
      "text": "based on the current direction of travel?"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 562800.0,
      "end_time": 563696.0,
      "text": "Well, here we go ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 563720.0,
      "end_time": 565496.0,
      "text": "and yes, there is some progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 565520.0,
      "end_time": 568216.0,
      "text": "Our top four countries are all hitting the SDG targets --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 568240.0,
      "end_time": 570456.0,
      "text": "some are moving forward quite quickly."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 570480.0,
      "end_time": 573856.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s not enough to really move us forward significantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 573880.0,
      "end_time": 576136.0,
      "text": "What we see is that for the world as a whole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 576160.0,
      "end_time": 581576.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re forecasting a score of around 85, 86 by 2030 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 581600.0,
      "end_time": 582800.0,
      "text": "not fast enough."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 583880.0,
      "end_time": 585856.0,
      "text": "Now, obviously this is not good news,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 585880.0,
      "end_time": 590136.0,
      "text": "but I think what this data also shows is that we could be doing a lot better."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 590160.0,
      "end_time": 592736.0,
      "text": "Water and sanitation is a solved problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 592760.0,
      "end_time": 595336.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about scaling that solution everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 595360.0,
      "end_time": 598256.0,
      "text": "So if we could accelerate progress in some of those countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 598280.0,
      "end_time": 599856.0,
      "text": "who are improving more slowly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 599880.0,
      "end_time": 601536.0,
      "text": "Nigeria, the Philippines, etc. --"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 601560.0,
      "end_time": 603640.0,
      "text": "then we could get a lot closer to the goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 604480.0,
      "end_time": 608896.0,
      "text": "Indeed, I think SDG 6 is probably the biggest opportunity"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 608920.0,
      "end_time": 611400.0,
      "text": "of all the SDGs for a step change."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 613920.0,
      "end_time": 615719.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s an area we could do better."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 616800.0,
      "end_time": 619616.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s look finally at an area where we are struggling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 619640.0,
      "end_time": 623415.0,
      "text": "which is what we call personal rights and inclusiveness."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 623440.0,
      "end_time": 626176.0,
      "text": "This is covering concepts across a range of SDGs."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 626200.0,
      "end_time": 630536.0,
      "text": "SDG 1 on poverty, SDG 5 on gender equality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 630560.0,
      "end_time": 632656.0,
      "text": "SDG 10 on inequality,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 632680.0,
      "end_time": 635160.0,
      "text": "SDG 11 on inclusive cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 635400.0,
      "end_time": 638695.0,
      "text": "and SDG 16 on peace and justice."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 638720.0,
      "end_time": 642536.0,
      "text": "So across those SDGs there are themes around rights and inclusiveness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 642560.0,
      "end_time": 645160.0,
      "text": "and those may seem less immediate or pressing"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 645400.0,
      "end_time": 647175.0,
      "text": "than things like hunger and disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 647200.0,
      "end_time": 652240.0,
      "text": "but rights and inclusion are critical to an agenda of no one left behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 653240.0,
      "end_time": 654955.0,
      "text": "So how are we doing on those issues?"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 655520.0,
      "end_time": 657536.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s start off with personal rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 657560.0,
      "end_time": 661815.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m going to do first is show you our big countries in 2015."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 661840.0,
      "end_time": 663560.0,
      "text": "So here they are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 663800.0,
      "end_time": 664976.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve put the USA and Japan back in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 665000.0,
      "end_time": 667176.0,
      "text": "so it&#39;s our 13 biggest countries in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 667200.0,
      "end_time": 669160.0,
      "text": "And we see a wide range of scores."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 669400.0,
      "end_time": 671976.0,
      "text": "The United States at the top with Japan hitting the goals;"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 672000.0,
      "end_time": 674136.0,
      "text": "China a long way behind."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 674160.0,
      "end_time": 676136.0,
      "text": "So what&#39;s been our direction of travel"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 676160.0,
      "end_time": 678656.0,
      "text": "on the rights agenda over the last three years?"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 678680.0,
      "end_time": 679935.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s have a look."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 679960.0,
      "end_time": 683560.0,
      "text": "Well, what we see is actually pretty ugly."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 683800.0,
      "end_time": 686976.0,
      "text": "The majority of the countries are standing still or moving backwards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 687000.0,
      "end_time": 690896.0,
      "text": "and big countries like Brazil, India, China, Bangladesh"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 690920.0,
      "end_time": 693479.0,
      "text": "have all seen significant declines."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 694240.0,
      "end_time": 695440.0,
      "text": "This is worrying."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 696480.0,
      "end_time": 699416.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s have a look now at inclusiveness."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 699440.0,
      "end_time": 701296.0,
      "text": "And inclusiveness is looking at things"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 701320.0,
      "end_time": 704560.0,
      "text": "like violence and discrimination against minorities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 704800.0,
      "end_time": 707216.0,
      "text": "gender equity, LGBT inclusion, etc..."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 707240.0,
      "end_time": 711536.0,
      "text": "And as a result, we see that the scores for our big countries are generally lower."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 711560.0,
      "end_time": 714550.0,
      "text": "Every country, rich and poor alike, is struggling"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 714800.0,
      "end_time": 716000.0,
      "text": "with building an inclusive society."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 716720.0,
      "end_time": 718416.0,
      "text": "But what&#39;s our direction of travel?"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 718440.0,
      "end_time": 720536.0,
      "text": "Are we building more inclusive countries?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 720560.0,
      "end_time": 722680.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s have a look -- progress to 2018."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 723280.0,
      "end_time": 725616.0,
      "text": "And again we see the world moving backwards:"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 725640.0,
      "end_time": 727376.0,
      "text": "most countries static,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 727400.0,
      "end_time": 729336.0,
      "text": "a lot of countries going backwards --"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 729360.0,
      "end_time": 731136.0,
      "text": "Bangladesh moving backwards --"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 731160.0,
      "end_time": 733695.0,
      "text": "but also, two of the countries that were leading --"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 733720.0,
      "end_time": 735336.0,
      "text": "Brazil and the United States --"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 735360.0,
      "end_time": 737176.0,
      "text": "have gone backwards significantly"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 737200.0,
      "end_time": 738560.0,
      "text": "over the last three years."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 739760.0,
      "end_time": 742256.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s sum this up now for the world as a whole."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 742280.0,
      "end_time": 745175.0,
      "text": "And what we see on personal rights for the whole world"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 745200.0,
      "end_time": 748816.0,
      "text": "is we&#39;re forecasting actually a decline in the score on personal rights"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 748840.0,
      "end_time": 750256.0,
      "text": "to about 60,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 750280.0,
      "end_time": 754520.0,
      "text": "and then this decline in the score of inclusiveness to about 42."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 755480.0,
      "end_time": 757936.0,
      "text": "Now, obviously these things can change quite quickly"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 757960.0,
      "end_time": 761896.0,
      "text": "with rights and with changes in law, changes in attitudes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 761920.0,
      "end_time": 764216.0,
      "text": "but we have to accept that on current trends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 764240.0,
      "end_time": 768120.0,
      "text": "this is probably the most worrying aspect of the SDGs."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 769720.0,
      "end_time": 771160.0,
      "text": "How I&#39;ve depressed you ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 771400.0,
      "end_time": 772336.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 772360.0,
      "end_time": 774976.0,
      "text": "I hope not because I think what we do see"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 775000.0,
      "end_time": 778416.0,
      "text": "is that progress is happening in a lot of places"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 778440.0,
      "end_time": 781536.0,
      "text": "and there are opportunities for accelerating progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 781560.0,
      "end_time": 785295.0,
      "text": "We are living in a world that is tantalizingly close"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 785320.0,
      "end_time": 791136.0,
      "text": "to ensuring that no one need die of hunger or malaria or diarrhea."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 791160.0,
      "end_time": 794376.0,
      "text": "If we can focus our efforts, mobilize resources,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 794400.0,
      "end_time": 796136.0,
      "text": "galvanize the political will,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 796160.0,
      "end_time": 798790.0,
      "text": "that step change is possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 799640.0,
      "end_time": 803415.0,
      "text": "But in focusing on those really basic, solvable SDGs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 803440.0,
      "end_time": 805736.0,
      "text": "we mustn&#39;t forget the whole package."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 805760.0,
      "end_time": 810856.0,
      "text": "The goals are an unwieldy set of indicators, goals and targets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 810880.0,
      "end_time": 814415.0,
      "text": "but they also include the challenges our world faces."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 814440.0,
      "end_time": 816936.0,
      "text": "The fact that the SDGs are focusing attention"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 816960.0,
      "end_time": 820976.0,
      "text": "on the fact that we face a crisis in personal rights and inclusiveness"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 821000.0,
      "end_time": 822520.0,
      "text": "is a positive."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 823200.0,
      "end_time": 824456.0,
      "text": "If we forget that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 824480.0,
      "end_time": 828496.0,
      "text": "if we choose to double down on the SDGs that we can solve,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 828520.0,
      "end_time": 834175.0,
      "text": "if we go for SDG à la carte and pick the most easy SDGs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 834200.0,
      "end_time": 837576.0,
      "text": "then we will have missed the point of the SDGs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 837600.0,
      "end_time": 839296.0,
      "text": "we will miss the goals"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 839320.0,
      "end_time": 842720.0,
      "text": "and we will have failed on the promise of the SDGs."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 843600.0,
      "end_time": 844816.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 844840.0,
      "end_time": 848480.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}